Corsicanto Designated Activity Company

Company Summary
Corsicanto Designated Activity Company was set up on Thursday the 17th of November 2011. Their current address is Dublin 2, and the company status is Normal. The company's current directors Patrick Joseph O'Sullivan, Joseph Thomas Kennedy and Conor Dalton have been the director of 6 other Irish companies between them; 1 of which is now closed.  Corsicanto Designated Activity Company has 1 shareholder. This Irish company shares its Eircode with at least 277 other companies.


Company Vitals


