	Article I

	: Purchase of Notes



	Subject to the terms set forth in this Agreement, at the Closing (as defined herein), the Undersigned hereby agrees to cause the Purchasers to
	purchase from the Company, and the Company hereby agrees to issue and sell to the Purchasers, the principal amount of the Notes set forth in

	Exhibit A

	for the cash purchase price specified in

	Exhibit A

	.


