	Closing

	) shall occur on a date (the 

	Closing Date

	) which the parties
	intend to be January 25, 2017. At the Closing, (a) each Purchaser shall deliver or cause to be delivered to the Company the Purchase Price specified on

	Exhibit A

	hereto and (b) upon receipt of the Purchase Price, the
	Company shall issue to each Purchaser the principal amount of Notes specified on

	Exhibit A

	hereto (collectively, the 

	Purchased Notes

